# 詞: 銀包

1. 你個銀包仲有冇錢？我哋去食飯啦！  
   Do you still have any cash in your wallet? Let’s go grab a bite!

2. 唔好將信用卡同現金放喺同一個銀包，萬一失左就慘啦！  
   Don’t keep your credit cards and cash in the same wallet — if you lose it, you’re screwed!

3. 佢個銀包好舊，但係仲用到，因為係阿媽送嘅生日禮物。  
   His wallet’s really old, but he still uses it ‘cause it was a birthday gift from his mum.

4. 你個銀包仲有冇五蚊紙？我個手機冇電，要搭巴士。  
   Do you still got any five-dollar notes? My phone’s dead — I need to catch the bus.

5. 佢成日將銀包放喺後袋，結果一朝坐低就「爆袋」，錢都飛左！  
   He always keeps his wallet in his back pocket — one day he sat down and it ripped open, and all his cash flew out!

6. 你個銀包有冇張八達通？我忘左帶，想搭地鐵。  
   Got your Octopus card with you? I forgot mine — need to catch the MTR.

7. 佢個銀包好扁，因為成日將錢用晒，仲要借錢度假。  
   His wallet’s always flat ‘cause he spends all his cash — even had to borrow money for his holiday.

8. 你個銀包有冇張舊鈔？我個收銀機唔識認新版五佰蚊。  
   Got any old notes? The cashier’s machine don’t recognize the new $500 notes.

9. 佢個銀包好重，因為成日攞住一疊收據同信用卡，真係煩死人。  
   His wallet’s so heavy ‘cause he always carries a stack of receipts and credit cards — it’s so annoying.

